com.android.dumprendertree2

Class TextResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.dumprendertree2.AbstractResult
      • com.android.dumprendertree2.TextResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<AbstractResult>

    public class TextResult
extends AbstractResult
    A result object for which the expected output is text. It does not have an image expected result.

    Created if layoutTestController.dumpAsText() was called.

    See Also:
